{
  "id": "adv_event_2206_02_01",
  "title": "1周年ドカン",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01-skr001.wav",
      "text": "{user}さーん！\n一年間、お疲れ様でした！",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01-ktn001.wav",
      "text": "お疲れ様でした！",
      "startTime": 5.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01-skr002.wav",
      "text": "この一年、いろんなことが\nありましたね！",
      "startTime": 7.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01-ktn002.wav",
      "text": "{user}さん\n覚えていますか？",
      "startTime": 11,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01-skr003.wav",
      "text": "サニピは沖縄に行ったなー！\n月ストの夏曲も良かったし！",
      "startTime": 13.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01-ktn003.wav",
      "text": "ありがとう。サニピも\nカウントダウン曲、良かった",
      "startTime": 18.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01-skr004.wav",
      "text": "あったあった。さとみさんの\n新しい一面が見れたし…",
      "startTime": 23.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01-ktn004.wav",
      "text": "あとはやっぱり…\nお姉ちゃんの誕生日",
      "startTime": 28.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01-skr005.wav",
      "text": "うん。すっごく思い出に\n残ってる",
      "startTime": 32.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01-ktn005.wav",
      "text": "きっと喜んでくれてると思う\n…ですよね？　マネージャー",
      "startTime": 35.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01-skr006.wav",
      "text": "…あれ？　そういえば\nなんで急にこんなことを？",
      "startTime": 41.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01-ktn006.wav",
      "text": "それもそうね…別に今日は\nなんでもない日だよね？",
      "startTime": 46.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01-skr007.wav",
      "text": "でも、日頃の感謝を\n伝えることは大事だよね",
      "startTime": 51.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01-ktn007.wav",
      "text": "うん\nそれだけは確かだと思う",
      "startTime": 55.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01-skr008.wav",
      "text": "じゃあ、改めて…",
      "startTime": 58.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01-ktn008.wav",
      "text": "マネージャーさん！　一年間\nありがとうございました！",
      "startTime": 61.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2206_02_01-ktn009.wav",
      "text": "これからも頑張りますので\nよろしくお願いします！",
      "startTime": 65.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}